{
  "stem": "5328.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he knew that I am alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we danced, all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We danced, and we drank, then we made up parties.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- we were just in heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not only me--I was Jewish, but I was between-- between Poles and Ukrainian people and also soldiers from-- French soldiers who were, like prisoners of war, they were working on the farms, too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- all of, us, we-- we took, then, from the German-- we took all the liquor and the [? speck ?] and the-- the meats and the cold cuts and-- and food, and we-- we made parties.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had parties 24 hours, day and night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just-- Also after the Americans came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Americans came in already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not until I came to-- about a month later, I-- I was going towards-- going home, like to Zdolbunow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it came to my mind if I-- there was Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't Poland, it was Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to my mind-- if I'll come to Russia, they wouldn't let me out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll have to stay there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was, with my father, hidden together, he tell-- he told me, my daughter, the war will finished.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hitler will-- will not win.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon as the war will finish, the only place you should go is to Israel or to America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They'll be open the doors for children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you can, go to-- if you-- to-- to Palestine or to America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave me the address to my uncle in America, and I kept it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember what my father told me that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go or to Israel, or to America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I'll come to Russia, they wouldn't let me out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I stopped in Poland, in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went down in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
